<p>"Open Source" should not be confused with the similar <strong>Free Software</strong>, which is defined by the <a href="https://www.fsf.org/">Free Software Foundation</a>. Generally, all Free Software is also Open Source, and the two camps often cooperate; however, the concepts are distinct! (The tags are merged here on DEV.to for simplicity, however.)</p>

<p>Open Source Hardware is <a href="https://www.oshwa.org/definition/">defined</a> and overseen by the <a href="https://www.oshwa.org/">Open Source Hardware Assocation</a></p>

